data.name: BtnHistoryPrune.ToolTip
data.value: Prune the song history. This will remove any song history entries that aren't in the library, cannot be found in storage, or are a stream not found in the playlist. The total number of song history entries is given in parentheses.

data.name: TxtBoxRandomHistoryUpdateInterval.ToolTip
data.value: Update Shuffle Play History after 1-60 seconds, or 0 for immediate update. Shuffle Play History is a list of songs played while in Shuffle Play Mode and is used when clicking the previous song button.
